spec_data.Name: texlive-bibleref-lds
spec_data.Description:
The package extends the bibleref-mouth package to support
references to the scriptures of The Church of Jesus Christ of
Latter-day Saints (LDS). The package requires bibleref-mouth to
run, and its reference syntax is the same as that of the parent
package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:40:29 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Bible references, including those to the scriptures of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter Day Saints
